title: Dune: Part Two
overview: Follow the mythic journey of Paul Atreides as he unites with Chani and the Fremen while on a warpath of revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, he endeavors to prevent a terrible future only he can foresee.

title: The Little Mermaid
overview: The youngest of King Triton's daughters, and the most defiant, Ariel longs to find out more about the world beyond the sea, and while visiting the surface, falls for the dashing Prince Eric. With mermaids forbidden to interact with humans, Ariel makes a deal with the evil sea witch, Ursula, which gives her a chance to experience life on land, but ultimately places her life - and her father's crown - in jeopardy.
tagline: Watch and you'll see, some day I'll be, part of your world!

title: Top Gun: Maverick
overview: After more than thirty years of service as one of the Navy's top aviators, Pete Mitchell is where he belongs, pushing the envelope as a courageous test pilot and dodging the advancement in rank that would ground him.
tagline: Feel the need... the need for speed.

title: Thor: Love and Thunder
overview: After his retirement is interrupted by Gorr the God Butcher, a galactic killer who seeks the extinction of the gods, Thor enlists the help of King Valkyrie, Korg, and ex-girlfriend Jane Foster, who now inexplicably wields Mjolnir as the Mighty Thor. Together, they embark upon a harrowing cosmic adventure to uncover the mystery of the God Butcher's vengeance and stop him before it's too late.
tagline: The one is not the only one.

title: Black Panther: Wakanda Forever
overview: Queen Ramonda, Shuri, M'Baku, Okoye and the Dora Milaje fight to protect their nation from intervening world powers in the wake of King T'Challa's death. As the Wakandans strive to embrace their next chapter, the heroes must band together with the help of War Dog Nakia and Everett Ross and forge a new path for the kingdom of Wakanda.

title: Everything Everywhere All at Once
overview: An aging Chinese immigrant is swept up in an insane adventure, where she alone can save the world by exploring other universes connecting with the lives she could have led.
tagline: The universe is so much bigger than you realize.

title: Inception
overview: A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O.
tagline: Your mind is the scene of the crime.

title: Interstellar
overview: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.
tagline: Mankind was born on Earth. It was never meant to die here.

title: The Dark Knight
overview: When the menace known as the Joker wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham, Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice.

title: Fight Club
overview: An insomniac office worker and a devil-may-care soap maker form an underground fight club that evolves into something much, much more.

title: Pulp Fiction
overview: The lives of two mob hitmen, a boxer, a gangster and his wife, and a pair of diner bandits intertwine in four tales of violence and redemption.
tagline: You won't know the facts until you've seen the fiction.

title: Forrest Gump
overview: The presidencies of Kennedy and Johnson, the Vietnam War, the Watergate scandal and other historical events unfold from the perspective of an Alabama man with an IQ of 75, whose only desire is to be reunited with his childhood sweetheart.
tagline: Life is like a box of chocolates...you never know what you're gonna get.

title: The Matrix
overview: Set in the 22nd century, The Matrix tells the story of a computer hacker who joins a group of underground insurgents fighting the vast and powerful computers who now rule the earth.

title: Joker
overview: In 1981 Gotham City, a struggling comedian, disregarded by society, turns to a life of crime and chaos, stirring a counter-cultural revolution against the wealthy.

title: Hamilton
overview: The real life of one of America's foremost founding fathers and first Secretary of the Treasury, Alexander Hamilton. Captured live on Broadway from the Richard Rodgers Theatre with the original Broadway cast.

title: The Batman
overview: When a sadistic serial killer begins murdering key political figures in Gotham, Batman is forced to investigate the city's hidden corruption and question his family's involvement.

title: Dune
overview: Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, must travel to the most dangerous planet in the universe to ensure the future of his family and his people. As malevolent forces explode into conflict over the planet's exclusive supply of the most precious resource in existence-a commodity capable of unlocking humanity's greatest potential-only those who can conquer their fear will survive.

title: Dungeons & Dragons: Honor Among Thieves
overview: A charming thief and a band of unlikely adventurers undertake an epic heist to retrieve a lost relic, but things go dangerously awry when they run afoul of the wrong people.
tagline: Who needs heroes when you have thieves?

title: John Wick: Chapter 4
overview: With the price on his head ever increasing, John Wick uncovers a path to defeating The High Table. But before he can earn his freedom, Wick must face off against a new enemy with powerful alliances across the globe and forces that turn old friends into foes.
tagline: No way back, one way out.

title: Avatar: The Way of Water
overview: Jake Sully lives with his newfound family formed on the extrasolar moon Pandora. Once a familiar threat returns to finish what was previously started, Jake must work with Neytiri and the army of the Na'vi race to protect their home.

title: Oppenheimer
overview: The story of American scientist J. Robert Oppenheimer and his role in the development of the atomic bomb.

title: Barbie
overview: Barbie and Ken are having the time of their lives in the colorful and seemingly perfect world of Barbie Land. However, when they get a chance to go to the real world, they soon discover the joys and perils of living among humans.

title: Mission: Impossible - Dead Reckoning Part One
overview: Ethan Hunt and his IMF team embark on their most dangerous mission yet: To track down a terrifying new weapon that threatens all of humanity before it falls into the wrong hands. With control of the future and the fate of the world at stake, and dark forces from Ethan's past closing in, a deadly race around the globe begins. Confronted by a mysterious, all-powerful enemy, Ethan is forced to consider that nothing can matter more than his mission - not even the lives of those he cares about most.
tagline: This is not just a mission. It's a race against time.

title: Stree 2
overview: The residents of Chanderi town live in constant fear of Stree, a female spirit who abducts men during a 4-day annual festival, leaving behind only their clothes. Vicky, a ladies' tailor, falls for a mysterious girl. His friends suspect she could be Stree.

title: Fighter
overview: Top IAF aviators handpicked from across the country come together for a mission that will make them heroes for a lifetime. They are now the first responders to any hostile activity, operating in and outside the country's borders.
tagline: Live for the nation, die for the nation.

title: Laapataa Ladies
overview: Two young brides get lost from a train. The chaos that ensues is both funny and moving in equal measure. A story about the search for the missing brides and the surprising places they end up.
tagline: Sometimes you have to get lost to find yourself.

title: Jawan
overview: A high-octane action thriller that outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in society.

title: Animal
overview: The son of a wealthy businessman learns about a plot to assassinate his father. He sets out on a path of revenge and destruction, which leads him to a world of violence and bloodshed.

title: Pathaan
overview: An Indian RAW agent, Pathaan, gets to know about a major attack planned by a mercenary group, led by a former RAW agent, Jim, who has gone rogue. With the help of an ISI agent, Rubina, Pathaan is on a mission to save his country.

title: RRR
overview: A fictitious story about two legendary revolutionaries and their journey away from home before they started fighting for their country in the 1920s.

title: Brahmastra Part One: Shiva
overview: This is the story of Shiva who sets out in search of love and self-discovery. During his journey, he has to face many evil forces that threaten our existence.

title: Drishyam 2
overview: 7 years after the case related to Vijay Salgaonkar and his family was closed, a series of unexpected events bring a truth to light that threatens to change everything for the Salgaonkars. Can Vijay save his family this time?

title: Gangubai Kathiawadi
overview: Duped and sold to a brothel, a young woman fearlessly reclaims her power, using underworld connections to rule her domain.
tagline: The queen of Mumbai's red-light district.

title: Sooryavanshi
overview: Sooryavanshi traces the acts and serious antics of DCP Veer Sooryavanshi, the chief of the Anti-Terrorism Squad in India.
The story of India's incredible cricket World Cup victory in 1983.
tagline: The story of India's greatest victory.

title: Shershaah
overview: The story of PVC awardee Indian soldier Capt. Vikram Batra, who shot to fame and became a household name during the Kargil War of 1999.

title: Mimi
overview: Mimi is a story of a young, feisty girl from a small town in Rajasthan who becomes a surrogate mother to make some quick money. The film follows her journey as she navigates the social stigma and the emotional rollercoaster of surrogacy.

title: Spider-Man: No Way Home
overview: With Spider-Man's identity now revealed, Peter asks Doctor Strange for help. When a spell goes wrong, dangerous foes from other worlds start to appear, forcing Peter to discover what it truly means to be Spider-Man.
tagline: The Multiverse is a concept about which we know frighteningly little.
